com.konakartadmin.app

Class AdminGeoZone

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.konakartadmin.app.AdminGeoZone

  • public class AdminGeoZone
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the AdminGeoZone class - it has geo zoneId, geo name, geo description.

    Note that there's 3 related tables: zones, geo_zones and zones_to_geo_zones "joins" them together.
